headlines.text:
This API allows you to interact with the growing viral social media platform TikTok. Since TikTok does not have an official API, you can use ours instead to do a large list of things including getting trending TikToks. 

You can use our API for a variety of projects including but not limited to the following
* A TikTok Compilation Bot
* A TikTok Clone
* TikTok Data Analysis
* And more!

What the API supports
* Trending TikToks
* A Specific User's TikTok's
* TikTok's under a specific hashtag
* TikTok's by a specific sound / music
* Trending Hashtags
* Trending Sounds / music
* And more!
